	* prescribing criteria for the sustainabilities of  forests;
	* prescribing indicators which may be used to measure the state of forest management and appropriate standards in relation to the indicators;
	* creating or promoting certification programmes and other incentives to encourage sustainable forest management; and
	* for the sustainable management of beekeeping.
	* The Minister shall, in prescribing criteria, indicators and standards under subsection (1), take into account economic, social and environmental conditions.
	* Criteria and indicators prescribed under subsection (1) may include those for determiningâ¢
